item.title: Who we are
item.dc:creator: bradweb
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row sp_top="100" sp_bottom="70" bg_type="image" bg_style="stretch" fixed_bg="no" enable_parallax="no" height="content" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" bg_overlay_dot="no" triangle_location="top" padding="medium" vpadding="medium" sp_left="40" sp_right="40" mtop="0" mbottom="0" mleft="0" mright="0" background_style="stretch" enable_border="" enable_bottom_border="" equal_height="" bg_overlay="" enable_triangle=""][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_column_text][dropcap]E[/dropcap]ntrepreneurship is the driving force of the world economy. But while entrepreneurs play a role in every layer of society, they don’t all receive the same access to capital markets.

Entrepreneurs invest the capital necessary for productivity growth, organize production into firms and industries, compete and cooperate to create and distribute goods and services to consumers in the most efficient and profitable manner.

Therefore access to capital is required to run a business. However, financial institutions generally focus on serving large corporations, while (micro,) small and medium enterprises (SME) face difficulties attracting the right amount of finance at the right time.

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_column_text]

We believe that the relationship between companies is the key to resolve the (M)SME finance problem. By introducing the Trefi Platfom we are changing the way how companies are financed.

The vision of Trefi is to resolve information asymmetry in finance of SME, whilst reducing cost. Solving the information asymmetry problem will revolutionize the financial services on offer to MSME.

The economic and banking importance of the (M)SME sector is well recognized in academic and policy literature. It is also acknowledged that these actors in the economy may be under-served, especially in terms of finance. This has led to significant debate on the best methods to serve this sector.

item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: bradweb
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: robgrimberg
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

Separated they live in Bookmarksgrove right at the coast of the Semantics, a large language ocean. A small river named Duden flows by their place and supplies it with the necessary regelialia. It is a paradisematic country, in which roasted parts of sentences fly into your mouth. Even the all-powerful Pointing has no control about the blind texts it is an almost unorthographic life One day however a small line of blind text by the name of Lorem Ipsum decided to leave for the far World of Grammar.

item.content:encoded:
[vc_row bottom_margin="yes" padding="large" full_width="stretch_row_content" vpadding="medium" sp_left="40" sp_right="40" sp_top="0" sp_bottom="0" mtop="0" mbottom="0" mleft="0" mright="0" enable_border="" enable_bottom_border="" bg_type="image" equal_height="" background_style="stretch" fixed_bg="no" enable_parallax="no" height="content" bg_overlay="" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" bg_overlay_dot="no" enable_triangle="" triangle_location="top"][vc_column width="2/3" ctype="current" p_top="0" p_bottom="0" p_left="0" p_right="0" color_scheme="" bg_overlay="" bg_overlay_color="" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" text_align="none"][vc_single_image image="10083" css_animation_delay="100" img_align="left" img_lightbox="" img_link_large="no" img_size="fullwidth"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" ctype="current" p_top="0" p_bottom="0" p_left="0" p_right="0" bg_overlay="" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" text_align="none"][vc_heading title="Partners" type="h3" style="default" bw="2" divider_height="2" divider_width="default" divider_color="dark" bc="dark" color="default" align="left" margin_bottom="20"][vc_accordion style="style 1" active_tab="1" disable_keyboard=""][vc_accordion_tab title="TRSB"][vc_column_text]The Receivable Standards Board provides a standard for financing receivables. Its mission is to:
  • Enable standards for customer credit and receivable finance that ease transactions
  • Ensure standards provide a fair environment to ease receivable finance for any size companies and financiers
  • Stimulate best practises in receivable finance to optimise financing of the supply chain
  • Stimulate the ease and efficiency of trade
TRSB enables the standardisation of receivable finance transactions to ease receivable finance transactions and liquefy trade.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="CTC"][vc_column_text] Capital Tool Company is the leading provider of receivable risk-based valuation tools and develops cutting edge financial solution technology to value credit and liquidity risks of receivables. CTC has developed the platform underlying Trefi and calibrates the Trefi risk models. [/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="You"][vc_column_text]At Trefi you will work in a high performance environment and be part of a company that is leading a change in the financial world. We value openness, collaboration, creativity and joint development. We present you with an unique opportunity to use and develop your skills in an environment where you can make a difference to the organisation, its products and its customers. Do you dream of:
  • working in a dynamic, sophisticated and entrepreneurial environment;
  • being part of a team driving the progress of our products, our company and our customers;
  • operating in a small team and having a high level of responsibility from day one;
  • working in an international environment with companies and financiers;
  • making use of the latest innovations in financing, IT and risk technology?
Than you are one click away from meeting us![/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Receivable management"][vc_column_text] Trefi receivable management partner assist customers to collect their receivables [/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Integration"][vc_column_text] Integration partners assist the client to connect to Trefi or integrate Trefi into their offering [/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Data and Risk"][vc_column_text] Data and risk partners collaborate with Trefi to deliver the best risk information [/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Credit Insurance"][vc_column_text] Credit Insurance partners provide access to their insurance products over the Trefi platform [/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Advisory"][vc_column_text] Advisory partner independently may help you get the most out of Trefi [/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]

item.dc:creator: bradweb
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row padding="medium" vpadding="medium" sp_left="40" sp_right="40" sp_top="0" sp_bottom="0" mtop="0" mbottom="0" mleft="0" mright="0" enable_border="" enable_bottom_border="" bg_type="image" equal_height="" background_style="stretch" fixed_bg="no" enable_parallax="no" height="content" bg_overlay="" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" bg_overlay_dot="no" enable_triangle="" triangle_location="top" background_color="#6b9080" color_scheme="scheme1"][vc_column width="1/1" ctype="current" p_top="40" p_bottom="0" p_left="0" p_right="0" color_scheme="" bg_overlay="" bg_overlay_color="" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" text_align="none"][vc_tour interval="0"][vc_tab title="Quantitative Analysts" tab_id="631c606d-581a-0" icon="80|fontawesome"][vc_heading title="Quantitative Analysts" type="h2" style="default" bw="2" divider_height="2" divider_width="default" divider_color="dark" bc="dark" color="default" align="left" margin_bottom="20"][vc_column_text]

We know that you have a strong analytical (academic) background and that you love data mining.

Of course you have been programming in Java, or is C++ your language?

 

Guess what, your skills can change the world.

 

In our case the world of finance.

Not only will you design, develop, implement and calibrate new models but actually have impact!

To tell you a little bit about our company:

What we do effects the life of business owners all over the world. We believe that entrepreneurship is important and that entrepreneurs should be stimulated to do and be known for what they do best.

But in order to be successful capital is required. That is no problem for corporates but small and medium enterprises face a lot of difficulties. So we built an amazing platform which stimulates entrepreneurs to do what they do best. The practical tools help them to present their business in a way that financiers understand the risk. But what the models do go way beyond that.

The G-20 decided the solution the Trefi platform provides was worth a price, so we received a medal out of the hands of Obama. But we want more.

We want to continuously improve our platform. We need your dedication to perform various research activities to discover, develop and document enhanced valuation models. Does stochastic optimisation, clustering algorithms, neural networks and simulation techniques make your heart sing?

Are you our new quantitative analyst? Can we stop searching and invite you for a cup of coffee or a beer?

Let us know!

[/vc_column_text][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Front-End Developers" tab_id="1442310923133-2-2"][vc_heading title="Front-End Developer" type="h2" style="default" bw="2" divider_height="2" divider_width="default" divider_color="dark" bc="dark" color="default" align="left" margin_bottom="20"][vc_column_text]

We know that you have a strong analytical background and that you love responsive development.

Of course you have been programming in PHP and are familiar with modern front-end frameworks (boothstrap. Jquery)

 

Guess what, your skills can change the world.

 

In our case the world of finance.

Not only will you design, develop and implement our front end but actually have impact!

To tell you a little bit about our company:

What we do effects the life of business owners all over the world. We believe that entrepreneurship is important and that entrepreneurs should be stimulated to do and be known for what they do best.

But in order to be successful capital is required. That is no problem for corporates but small and medium enterprises face a lot of difficulties. So we built an amazing platform which stimulates entrepreneurs to do what they do best. The practical tools help them to present their business in a way that financiers understand the risk. But what the models do go way beyond that.

The G-20 decided the solution the Trefi platform provides was worth a price, so we received a medal out of the hands of Obama. But we want more.

We want to continuously improve our platform. We need your dedication to make the UX of our customers amazing? Does cross browser development and testing make your heart sing?

Are you our new front-end developer? Can we stop searching and invite you for a cup of coffee or a beer?

Let’s meet!

[/vc_column_text][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Internships" tab_id="a6718833-a5b4-6"][vc_heading title="Internships" type="h2" style="default" bw="2" divider_height="2" divider_width="default" divider_color="dark" bc="dark" color="default" align="left" margin_bottom="20"][vc_column_text]At Trefi we always make room for pro-active students who want to learn from experience. We strongly believe in co-creating an environment in which we can learn from one another.   We value openness, collaboration, creativity and joint development.   We present you with an unique opportunity to use and develop your skills in an environment where you can make a difference to the organisation, its products and its customers.  
We are particularly interested in meeting design, it and marketing-communication enthusiasts!
  Do you wish to:  
  • work in a dynamic, sophisticated and entrepreneurial environment;
  • be part of a team driving the progress of our products, our company and our customers;
  • work in an international environment with companies and financiers;
  • make use of the latest innovations in financing, IT and risk technology?
  Let us know so we can create a spot for you![/vc_column_text][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Product Managers" tab_id="1442676151156-3-8"][vc_heading title="Product Managers" type="h2" style="default" bw="2" divider_height="2" divider_width="default" divider_color="dark" bc="dark" color="default" align="left" margin_bottom="20" icon="361|fontawesome"][vc_column_text]We are looking for project manager / developers to implement with customers and design and implement new features based on customer requests and our product vision. In this role you will have the following responsibilities:
  • Work with clients to implement the product
  • Analyse user requirements and usage
  • Develop the new features in our system
  • Specify test cases and perform tests
You will be able to demonstrate:
  • Strong communication skills
  • Strong information analysis skills and business process oriented skills
  • Subject matter understanding
  • Development skills in PHP
[/vc_column_text][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Business Development" tab_id="1442676256053-4-10"][vc_heading title="Business Development" type="h2" style="default" bw="2" divider_height="2" divider_width="default" divider_color="dark" bc="dark" color="default" align="left" margin_bottom="20"][vc_column_text]We are looking for customer relationship managers to sell to financiers and large companies. You will be responsible for generating new revenue, exploring business opportunities, growing business, develop customer relationship and ensure customer satisfaction. As sales manager you will:
  • Achieve revenue targets
  • Originate new customer and ensure customer retention
  • Identify and start relationships with new advisory partners
  • Work with our customers and advisory partners to ensure satisfaction
  • Manage execution of customer projects
  • Attend industry events
You will be able to demonstrate:
  • In depth understanding of the corporate treasury and (investment) banking
  • In depth understanding how our products can create value for the customers
  • Ability to master complex sales processes
  • Experience in structured finance technique
  • Effectively executed deals
  • Excellent communication and presentation skills
  • Enthusiasm
  • Entrepreneurial spirit
  • At least five years relevant experience
.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tab][vc_tab title="Security management" tab_id="1442676385273-5-9"][vc_heading title="Security Management" type="h1" style="default" bw="2" divider_height="2" divider_width="default" divider_color="dark" bc="dark" color="default" align="left" margin_bottom="20"][vc_column_text]As security manager you are responsible for ensuring the continued confidentiality and integrity of the customers information. You will be controlling and maintaining the ISO 27001 information security policy and procedures.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tab][/vc_tour][vc_gap height="40" hide_under=""][/vc_column][/vc_row]

Negotiate more finance from your suppliers, resolve disputes with your suppliers, make easy payments and get finance on your invoices.

Typical size in developed markets up to €2m in sales or €250,000 in working capital requirements and up to $50k in emerging markets.

item.content:encoded:
[vc_row sp_top="120" sp_bottom="90" bg_type="image" bg_style="stretch" fixed_bg="no" enable_parallax="no" height="content" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" bg_overlay_dot="no" triangle_location="top" css=".vc_custom_1425559385239{background-color: #ffffff !important;}" vpadding="medium" sp_left="40" sp_right="40" background_style="stretch" padding="medium" mtop="0" mbottom="0" mleft="0" mright="0" enable_border="" enable_bottom_border="" background_color="#ffffff" equal_height="" bg_overlay="" enable_triangle=""][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_row_inner padding="large"][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_heading title="Trefi belief" type="h3" style="default" divider_width="parent" divider_color="light" color="default" align="left" margin_bottom="35" bw="2" divider_height="2" bc="dark"][vc_column_text]

At Trefi we believe that companies should have access to finance in accordance with the quality of their products and services.

Therefore we provide tools to companies to improve the relationships with the companies’ buyers and suppliers and improve the risk profile.

Therefore we provide financiers tools to provide the right amount of finance at the right time to the right company.

The vision of Trefi is to resolve information asymmetry in finance of SME, whilst reducing cost. Solving the information asymmetry problem will revolutionize the financing on offer to MSME.

We want to make the product as accessible as possible. Therefore we work with financiers and partners to distribute the Trefi promise.

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_toggle style="default" title="Who is Trefi?" open="false" size="md"]

Trefi is a not for profit foundation with the vision to resolve working capital problems.

Trefi is managed by a board that represents the companies and financiers on the platform.

Trefi believes in creating and maintaining a sustainable partner network to maximize impact.

[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title="How does Trefi work?" style="default" size="md" open="false" el_id="1440166462039-b479cabe-8c6a"]

Trefi provides companies tools to improve the financial relationship with its buyers and suppliers, ensuring and liquefying trade.

Trefi allows financiers to provide finance at low cost and risk. Financiers may integrate Trefi in their own offering or use the Trefi platform. 

[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title="What is in it for me?" style="default" size="md" open="false"]

Trefi provides tools to enable companies to optimise their working capital, reduce their risk profile and stimulate their growth.

Trefi provides tools for financiers to enable them to provide the right amount of finance at the right time. The system is completely automated which means that a financier can be up and running in a day. Trefi can also be deeply integrated into the financier’s online offering and back-office.

Trefi provides several opportunities for investors. By reducing risk and costs Trefi offers investment managers propositions with offering unprecedented risk-return on investment in SME finance.

[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle style="default" title="How do I use Trefi" open="false" size="md"]

Companies can be up and running in a day:

  • Sign up on Trefi
  • Connect your ERP to Trefi or start sending invoices using Trefi
  • Provide information about you and your company
  • Sign the finance contract
  • Accept the financing offer of your choice

Financiers:

  • Contact us to subscribe to the platform
  • Sign the documentation
  • Start financing or start integration into proprietary offerings
[/vc_toggle][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner vpadding="medium2" padding="medium2"][vc_column_inner el_class="" width="1/3"][vc_services_box title="Accessible" icon_style="style1" icon_radius="50%" icon_size="large" icon_c="#2d2d2d" icon_bgc="#c5a47e" radius="5px" vpadding="55px" hpadding="40px" bg_front="#d8f0ff" bg_flip="#d8f0ff" c_flip="#444444" c_content_flip="#444444" icon="36|fontawesome" desc="Trefi enables access to finance based on quality of products and services " bc_front="#d8f0ff" c_front="#444444" c_content="#444444" bc_flip="#d8f0ff" title_flip="Accessible"] While using the Trefi tools companies improve their cash flow, reduce risk on customers and improve supplier relationships while focusing on the core of their business. [/vc_services_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="" width="1/3"][vc_services_box title="Low Risks" icon_style="style1" icon_radius="50%" icon_size="large" icon_c="#2d2d2d" icon_bgc="#c5a47e" radius="5px" vpadding="55px" hpadding="40px" bg_front="#d8f0ff" bc_front="#d8f0ff" c_front="#444444" c_content="#444444" bg_flip="#d8f0ff" bc_flip="#d8f0ff" c_flip="#444444" c_content_flip="#444444" icon="91|fontawesome" desc="Trefi achieves low risk by enabling finance at the right time and in the right amount" title_flip="Low Risks"] By sharing the knowledge that companies have about their buyers and suppliers, Trefi creates timely information that make financial decisions more informed and fast. [/vc_services_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="" width="1/3"][vc_services_box title="Low Costs" title_flip="Low Costs" icon_style="style1" icon_radius="50%" icon_size="large" icon_c="#2d2d2d" icon_bgc="#c5a47e" radius="5px" vpadding="55px" hpadding="40px" bg_front="#d8f0ff" bc_front="#d8f0ff" c_front="#444444" c_content="#444444" bg_flip="#d8f0ff" bc_flip="#d8f0ff" c_flip="#444444" c_content_flip="#444444" icon="104|fontawesome" desc="Trefi achieves low cost by enabling collaboration between companies and between companies and financiers"] Trefi creates value by removing risk and duplication of work. The benefits are shared by participating companies, financiers and partners [/vc_services_box][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner vpadding="medium2" padding="medium2"][vc_column_inner el_class="" width="1/3"][vc_services_box title="Private and secure" icon_style="style1" icon_radius="50%" icon_size="large" icon_c="#2d2d2d" icon_bgc="#c5a47e" radius="5px" vpadding="55px" hpadding="40px" bg_front="#d8f0ff" bc_front="#d8f0ff" c_front="#444444" c_content="#444444" bg_flip="#d8f0ff" bc_flip="#d8f0ff" c_flip="#444444" c_content_flip="#444444" icon="9|fontawesome" desc="Trefi treats all information entrusted confidential. Only with the consent of the company information is shared." title_flip="Private and secure"]The governance of Trefi ensures the continued privacy of data. Trefi operates a highly secure system infrastructure. Trefi operates in accordance with ISO 27001, the standard for information security availability and integrity[/vc_services_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="" width="1/3"][vc_services_box title="Integrated" icon_style="style1" icon_radius="50%" icon_size="large" icon_c="#2d2d2d" icon_bgc="#c5a47e" radius="5px" vpadding="55px" hpadding="40px" bg_front="#d8f0ff" bc_front="#d8f0ff" c_front="#444444" c_content="#444444" bg_flip="#d8f0ff" bc_flip="#d8f0ff" c_flip="#444444" c_content_flip="#444444" desc="Trefi integrates with other information systems." icon="56|fontawesome" title_flip="Integrated"] Companies and financiers may integrate Trefi into their IT platform and choose which functionality of Trefi is used.[/vc_services_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="" width="1/3"][vc_services_box title="Sustainable" icon_style="style1" icon_radius="50%" icon_size="large" icon_c="#2d2d2d" icon_bgc="#c5a47e" radius="5px" vpadding="55px" hpadding="40px" bg_front="#d8f0ff" bc_front="#d8f0ff" c_front="#444444" c_content="#444444" bg_flip="#d8f0ff" bc_flip="#d8f0ff" c_flip="#444444" c_content_flip="#444444" desc="Trefi collaborates with financiers, companies and its partners" icon="208|fontawesome" title_flip="Sustainable"] By reinvesting all income into platform enhancement and by collaborating with companies, financiers and its partners Trefi will deliver what is needed, sustainably. [/vc_services_box][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row section_type="full-width" sp_top="0" sp_bottom="0" bg_type="image" background_style="stretch" fixed_bg="no" enable_parallax="no" height="content" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" bg_overlay_dot="no" triangle_location="top" equal_height="yes" padding="small2" vpadding="small2" sp_left="40" sp_right="40" mtop="0" mbottom="10" mleft="10" mright="10" enable_border="" enable_bottom_border="" bg_overlay="" enable_triangle=""][vc_column width="1/2" p_top="110" p_bottom="110" background_image="9530" bg_overlay="yes" bg_overlay_color="#4f5051" bg_overlay_opacity="0.85" p_left="0" p_right="0" text_align="none" ctype="boxed"][vc_box opacity="1" br_width="1" color_scheme="scheme1" padding="0 10%" br_top="" br_bottom="" hide_under=""][vc_heading title="For Companies" type="h2" style="default" bw="2" divider_height="2" divider_width="default" divider_color="dark" bc="dark" color="default" align="left" margin_bottom="20"][vc_column_text]With Trefi :
  • Your company will increase access to finance
  • Your company will have more flexibility with payment terms, resulting in more satisfied clients

item.dc:creator: bradweb
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row padding="medium" vpadding="medium" color_scheme="scheme1" sp_left="40" sp_right="40" sp_top="110" sp_bottom="130" mtop="0" mbottom="0" mleft="0" mright="0" enable_border="" enable_bottom_border="" bg_type="image" equal_height="" background_style="stretch" fixed_bg="no" enable_parallax="no" height="content" bg_overlay="yes" bg_overlay_color="#bae8ff" bg_overlay_opacity="0.5" bg_overlay_dot="no" enable_triangle="" triangle_location="top" background_image="9815"][vc_column width="1/1" ctype="current" p_top="40px" p_bottom="0" p_left="0" p_right="0" bg_overlay="" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" text_align="center"][vc_heading title="Financiers use Trefi to generate sustainable competitive advantage reducing risk, reducing operational cost, reducing funding cost and improving customer satisfaction." type="h3" style="default" bw="2" divider_height="2" divider_width="default" divider_color="dark" bc="dark" color="default" align="center" margin_bottom="20"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding="large" sp_top="90" sp_bottom="10" bg_type="image" background_style="stretch" fixed_bg="no" enable_parallax="no" height="content" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" bg_overlay_dot="no" triangle_location="top" background_color="#ffffff" triangle_color="#f7f7f7" vpadding="medium" sp_left="40" sp_right="40" mtop="0" mbottom="0" mleft="0" mright="0" enable_border="" enable_bottom_border="" equal_height="" bg_overlay="" enable_triangle=""][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_gap height="20" hide_under="tablet,mobile"][vc_heading title="Trefi for Banks" type="h3" style="default" divider_width="default" divider_color="dark" color="default" align="left" margin_bottom="25" bw="2" divider_height="2" bc="dark"][vc_column_text]

Banks use Trefi to reduce MSME finance costs including:

  • Capital cost - Trefi realised savings up to 85% with the same client and the same amount of finance
  • Risk cost - Trefi realised risk cost savings up to 85%
  • Operational cost - down up to 50% compared to traditional secured lending
Banks may integrate Trefi in their other online offering, operate powered by Trefi or provide funding lines to other financiers on the platform. By deploying the capital released, banks may increase the amount of finance provided to clients.[/vc_column_text][vc_gap height="40"][vc_button style="alternate" align="none" title="Contact us" target="_self" icon_align="right" icon_ds="hover" icon_size="normal" size="default" href="/contact" color_style="default" acolor="#555555" acolor_hover="#444444" bw="0" br="small" lb=""][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_gallery type="carousel" padding="narrow" columns="2" images="9642" img_size="thumb-large" onclick="link_image" custom_links_target="_self" vpadding="narrow" autoplay="" grey="" show_metadata=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding="large" sp_top="90" sp_bottom="10" bg_type="image" background_style="stretch" fixed_bg="no" enable_parallax="no" height="content" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" bg_overlay_dot="no" triangle_location="top" background_color="#f7f7f7" triangle_color="#ffffff" vpadding="medium" sp_left="40" sp_right="40" mtop="0" mbottom="0" mleft="0" mright="0" enable_border="" enable_bottom_border="" equal_height="" bg_overlay="" enable_triangle=""][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_gallery type="carousel" padding="narrow" columns="2" images="10111" img_size="thumb-large" onclick="link_image" custom_links_target="_self" vpadding="narrow" autoplay="" grey="" show_metadata=""][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_gap height="20" hide_under="tablet,mobile"][vc_heading title="Trefi for Factoring Companies" type="h3" style="default" bw="2" divider_height="2" divider_width="default" divider_color="dark" bc="dark" color="default" align="left" margin_bottom="25"][vc_column_text]

Factoring companies can move into the new era of invoice based finance with Trefi. Trefi offers an operational platform that covers all IT needs, including client interfaces for invoicing and for confirming, risk management on clients and debtors, back office, collections and more. With Trefi, factoring companies typically reduce operational cost by 75%.

Trefi offers access to capital markets through its proven capital markets program capabilities. Factoring companies may reduce funding cost and increase access to finance.

[/vc_column_text][vc_gap height="40"][vc_button style="alternate" align="none" title="Contact us" target="_self" icon_align="right" icon_ds="hover" icon_size="normal" size="default" href="/contact" color_style="default" acolor="#555555" acolor_hover="#444444" bw="0" br="small" lb=""][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/1" ctype="current" p_top="0" p_bottom="0" p_left="0" p_right="0" color_scheme="" bg_overlay="" bg_overlay_color="" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" text_align="none"][vc_column_text] [/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding="large" vpadding="medium" sp_left="40" sp_right="40" sp_top="90" sp_bottom="10" mtop="0" mbottom="0" mleft="0" mright="0" enable_border="" enable_bottom_border="" bg_type="image" equal_height="" background_style="stretch" fixed_bg="no" enable_parallax="no" height="content" bg_overlay="" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" bg_overlay_dot="no" enable_triangle="" triangle_color="#f7f7f7" triangle_location="top" background_color="#ffffff"][vc_column width="1/2" ctype="current" p_top="0" p_bottom="0" p_left="0" p_right="0" color_scheme="" bg_overlay="" bg_overlay_color="" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" text_align="none"][vc_gap height="20" hide_under="tablet,mobile"][vc_heading title="Trefi for Fund Manager" type="h3" style="default" bw="2" divider_height="2" divider_width="default" divider_color="dark" bc="dark" color="default" align="left" margin_bottom="25"][vc_column_text]With its unique complete operations Trefi can offer fund management efficient participation in the financing of working capital. Trefi has online customer origination and onboarding capabilities, managed by partners. The platform provides portfolio management capabilities and liability optimization to maximise return on investment.[/vc_column_text][vc_gap height="40" hide_under=""][vc_button style="alternate" size="default" color_style="default" color="" color_hover="" acolor="#555555" acolor_hover="#444444" bw="0" bcolor="" bcolor_hover="" br="small" align="none" title="Contact us" target="_self" lb="" icon="" icon_align="right" icon_size="normal" icon_style="" icon_c="" icon_c_hover="" icon_bc="" icon_bgc="" icon_bgc_hover="" icon_ds="hover" href="/contact"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" ctype="current" p_top="0" p_bottom="0" p_left="0" p_right="0" color_scheme="" bg_overlay="" bg_overlay_color="" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" text_align="none"][vc_gallery type="carousel" padding="narrow" vpadding="narrow" columns="2" autoplay="" grey="" images="9825" img_size="thumb-large" onclick="link_image" show_metadata="" custom_links_target="_self"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding="large" sp_top="90" sp_bottom="10" bg_type="image" background_style="stretch" fixed_bg="no" enable_parallax="no" height="content" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" bg_overlay_dot="no" triangle_location="top" background_color="#f7f7f7" triangle_color="#ffffff" vpadding="medium" sp_left="40" sp_right="40" mtop="0" mbottom="0" mleft="0" mright="0" enable_border="" enable_bottom_border="" equal_height="" bg_overlay="" enable_triangle=""][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_gallery type="carousel" padding="narrow" columns="2" images="10116" img_size="thumb-large" onclick="link_image" custom_links_target="_self" vpadding="narrow" autoplay="" grey="" show_metadata=""][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_gap height="20" hide_under="tablet,mobile"][vc_heading title="Trefi for Credit Unions" type="h3" style="default" divider_width="default" divider_color="dark" color="default" align="left" margin_bottom="25" bw="2" divider_height="2" bc="dark"][vc_column_text]

Trefi provides an administrative facility for credit unions that provide working capital. The union may decide to what level the risk of participating companies is shared among the union.

Trefi provides access to senior finance for the union.

Finance cost as low as Euribor + 2.5% have been achieved for small members of unions on the Trefi Platform in this way.

By using the Trefi platform the union gets access to the Trefi risk management capabilities that may be used for decisions on other types of finance.

[/vc_column_text][vc_gap height="40"][vc_button style="alternate" align="none" title="Contact us" target="_self" icon_align="right" icon_ds="hover" icon_size="normal" size="default" href="/contact" color_style="default" acolor="#555555" acolor_hover="#444444" bw="0" br="small" lb=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding="medium" vpadding="medium" color_scheme="scheme1" sp_left="40" sp_right="40" sp_top="110" sp_bottom="80" mtop="0" mbottom="0" mleft="0" mright="0" enable_border="" enable_bottom_border="" bg_type="image" equal_height="" background_style="stretch" fixed_bg="no" enable_parallax="no" height="content" bg_overlay="yes" bg_overlay_color="#2d2d2d" bg_overlay_opacity="0.92" bg_overlay_dot="no" enable_triangle="" triangle_location="top"][vc_column width="1/1" ctype="current" p_top="0" p_bottom="0" p_left="0" p_right="0" color_scheme="" bg_overlay="" bg_overlay_color="" bg_overlay_opacity="0.4" text_align="none"][vc_heading title="Supporting receivable finance from customer origination to work-out" type="h1" style="default" bw="2" divider_height="2" divider_width="default" divider_color="dark" bc="dark" color="default" align="center" margin_bottom="80"][vc_feature_boxes columns="5" padding="large" vpadding="medium" style="style1" height="50" bg_color="#ffffff" bg_radius="yes" border_width="1" ip_top="40" ip_left="40" bg_shadow="" box_style="style3" icon_side="left" fc_align="yes" fi_align="yes" divider="" di_color="light" di_style="2px" di_type="tiny" icon_style="style3" icon_size="extra-large" icon_bw="1" icon_br="50%" icon_c="#ffffff" icon_bgc="#6b9080" icon_bgc_hover="#bae8ff" bg_opacity="1" inner_hpadding="medium" inner_vpadding="medium" icon_c_opc="1" icon_c_hover_opc="1" icon_bc_opacity="1" icon_bgc_opacity="1" icon_bgc_opacity_hover="1"][vc_feature_box ftarget="_self" itarget="_self" title="Customer Relationship Management" ttarget="_self" title_heading="h4" css_animation_delay="100" css_animation_type="box" icon="346|fontawesome"]

A CRM designed to support the process to sign up prospects, to efficiently onboard customers, to credit approve and disburse finance and to monitor customer performance

[/vc_feature_box][vc_feature_box ftarget="_self" itarget="_self" title="Risk Management" ttarget="_self" title_heading="h4" css_animation_delay="100" css_animation_type="box" icon="33|fontawesome"]

Trefis unique risk management capabilities ensure that the customer get the right amount of finance at the right time to minimise Exposure at Default (EAD)

[/vc_feature_box][vc_feature_box ftarget="_self" itarget="_self" title="Back-Office" ttarget="_self" title_heading="h4" css_animation_delay="100" css_animation_type="box" icon="11|fontawesome"]

Trefi provides a complete settlement and accounting infrastructure for financiers

[/vc_feature_box][vc_feature_box ftarget="_self" itarget="_self" title="Collection and Work-Out" ttarget="_self" title_heading="h4" css_animation_delay="100" css_animation_type="box" icon="109|fontawesome"]

The Collection and Work out tools incorporated in Trefi support from collection to workout from full outsourcing to standby arrangements. Uniquely Trefi provides collaborative collection with the customer and collection specialists. The collection tools are designed to minimise the Loss Given Default (LGD)

[/vc_feature_box][vc_feature_box ftarget="_self" itarget="_self" title="Capital Markets Access" ttarget="_self" title_heading="h4" css_animation_delay="100" css_animation_type="box" icon="19|fontawesome"]

The Trefi platform allows attracting senior and mezzanine finance from capital markets and money markets in an efficient way, removing funding and capital constraints

[/vc_feature_box][/vc_feature_boxes][vc_heading title="Taking the new risk information beyond working capital" type="h1" style="default" bw="2" divider_height="2" divider_width="default" divider_color="dark" bc="dark" color="default" align="center" margin_bottom="80"][vc_feature_boxes columns="3" padding="large" vpadding="medium" style="style1" height="50" bg_color="#ffffff" bg_radius="yes" border_width="1" ip_top="40" ip_left="40" bg_shadow="" box_style="style3" icon_side="left" fc_align="yes" fi_align="yes" divider="" di_color="light" di_style="2px" di_type="tiny" icon_style="style3" icon_size="extra-large" icon_bw="1" icon_br="50%" icon_c="#ffffff" icon_bgc="#6b9080" icon_bgc_hover="#bae8ff" bg_opacity="1" inner_hpadding="medium" inner_vpadding="medium" icon_c_opc="1" icon_c_hover_opc="1" icon_bc_opacity="1" icon_bgc_opacity="1" icon_bgc_opacity_hover="1"][vc_feature_box ftarget="_self" itarget="_self" title="Probability of Default IRB PD" ttarget="_self" title_heading="h4" css_animation_delay="100" css_animation_type="box" icon="111|fontawesome"]

Trefi provides top class Probability of Default measures, which may easily be integrated into loan origination systems.

[/vc_feature_box][vc_feature_box ftarget="_self" itarget="_self" title="Securitisation Administration" ttarget="_self" title_heading="h4" css_animation_delay="100" css_animation_type="box" icon="126|fontawesome"]

Trefi provides trade receivable securitisation administration and risk assessment services. 

[/vc_feature_box][vc_feature_box ftarget="_self" itarget="_self" title="Treasury & Portfolio Management" ttarget="_self" title_heading="h4" css_animation_delay="100" css_animation_type="box" icon="104|fontawesome"]

The portfolio management tools provide tools to understand portfolio risk of each customer. Banks may integrate their loan portfolios in the Trefi platform

[/vc_feature_box][/vc_feature_boxes][/vc_column][/vc_row]

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: Trefi is the platform that enables providing finance at the right time, in the right amount, at low cost and with low risk.

The portfolio underlying this bond program is managed by Netwerk Financiering BV.

The portfolio invests in Dutch SME receivables.

A BBB Credit Rating has been obtained from Creditreform for the senior program and B for the mezzanine instrument.

The program is listed on Alternext.

You may invest in this bond program through your online broker (Alex, Binckbank) or by subscribing to Trefi as investor.

The portfolio is managed by Redfin SAC, a specialised SME finance company.

item.title: Markup: Text Alignment
item.dc:creator: bradweb
item.content:encoded:
Default

This is a paragraph. It should not have any alignment of any kind. It should just flow like you would normally expect. Nothing fancy. Just straight up text, free flowing, with love. Completely neutral and not picking a side or sitting on the fence. It just is. It just freaking is. It likes where it is. It does not feel compelled to pick a side. Leave him be. It will just be better that way. Trust me.

Left Align

This is a paragraph. It is left aligned. Because of this, it is a bit more liberal in it's views. It's favorite color is green. Left align tends to be more eco-friendly, but it provides no concrete evidence that it really is. Even though it likes share the wealth evenly, it leaves the equal distribution up to justified alignment.

Center Align

This is a paragraph. It is center aligned. Center is, but nature, a fence sitter. A flip flopper. It has a difficult time making up its mind. It wants to pick a side. Really, it does. It has the best intentions, but it tends to complicate matters more than help. The best you can do is try to win it over and hope for the best. I hear center align does take bribes.

Right Align

This is a paragraph. It is right aligned. It is a bit more conservative in it's views. It's prefers to not be told what to do or how to do it. Right align totally owns a slew of guns and loves to head to the range for some practice. Which is cool and all. I mean, it's a pretty good shot from at least four or five football fields away. Dead on. So boss.

Justify Align

This is a paragraph. It is justify aligned. It gets really mad when people associate it with Justin Timberlake. Typically, justified is pretty straight laced. It likes everything to be in it's place and not all cattywampus like the rest of the aligns. I am not saying that makes it better than the rest of the aligns, but it does tend to put off more of an elitist attitude.

item.title: Frederik Redelé
item.dc:creator: bradweb
item.content:encoded: Trefi is build for scale. Its quality control measures exceed anything I have seen in the financial markets and far beyond regulators requirements. Companies can trust their cash flow is safe with Trefi. Banks and fund managers using the platform can achieve lower funding cost rapidly by using Trefi or integrating Trefi in their offering.

item.title: Rob Grimberg
item.dc:creator: bradweb
item.content:encoded: When I was working in the bank on models for capital management, I saw a huge potential in the supply chain data. By a combination of big data techniques and incentives for companies, we have been able to deliver some of the most timely and predictive risk assessments. Helping quality business to grow makes me proud.

item.title: Sir Robert Malpas
item.dc:creator: bradweb
item.content:encoded: It is impressive how the Trefi team has engineered a platform that helps companies to manage order to cash and invoices to payment. With the liquidity this brings companies can focus on their core.

item.title: Hessel Lindenbergh
item.dc:creator: bradweb
item.content:encoded:
Trefi is an initiative each bank should look at. Its risk and cost savings and the tools for customers provide a huge competitive advantage.
I foresee a future where there are no SME finance problems.
I foresee a future where access to working capital for SME is the same as for Large Corporations.
